data.description: Looking for a Lakefront property with extraordinary Lakeview's? This beautiful two-bedroom, two-bath has a 180-degree view from all rooms that is hard-to-find on the lake with .58 acres plus 40 ft of lakefront. Watch 4th of July fireworks from your balcony, launch a kayak from your beach, or just take in the radiant sunrises and watch the otters, swans, and other wildlife that like to call your backyard home. This house has been well maintained and updated, ready for you to move right in. High ceilings and an open floor plan makes it easy for entertaining while taking in the views. The living room has a sliding glass door to the balcony with a Trex deck, and the master bedroom has its own sliding glass door with access to the deck. The house has a modern feel with new fixtures and metallic paint to let the reflection from the lake provide plenty of light inside. The bedroom downstairs also has a great view of the lake and has been used as an office. The house comes with most furniture and Starlink Wi-Fi which provides reliable internet services. With an electric front gate and security cameras, this house has been updated with the modern conveniences you expect. Plenty of space for parking RVs, boats, and jet skis. This would be a great Airbnb, vacation home, or forever home. Live your BEST life on the lake. Lakefront homes like these do not come on the market often. Great Location and close to shopping, restaurants, and Sutter Lakeside Hospital is within a few minute's drive. Note: Dock and Piers belong to neighbors.
